{"tid":2346880,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"試當真張新相勁有幻影旅團Feel，我覺得係有極深的寓意","createTime":"2020-12-30T14:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T16:58:36.000Z","uid":38539,"like":9,"dislike":146,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"54d07bdb2f6724fb602b00b13b8013e271630a43","tid":2346880,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TNhTzkH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTNhTzkH.png&h=72f3027b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpbMUkH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpbMUkH.jpg&h=c7ae477f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢哋係呢個時間點上po張相出嚟，<br />\n係想表達出雖然佢哋最近受到好多爭議，<br />\n但試當真的本質就等同幻影旅團一樣，<br />\n每個成員都係帶有濃厚的個人作風，<br />\n佢哋組合而成為一個不受約束的組織，<br />\n就有如係馬路上無視影快相機奔馳直衝天際，<br />\n而且實力強橫完全唔怕俾其他人挑釁，<br />\n就連業界一流的老haters都好難對佢哋出手，<br />\n相反佢哋仲好享受呢種處於危險的輿論戰之中。<br />\n<br />\n呀修就係團長，旅團的領導人。同樣有銳利的思考能力和出眾的洞察力，並且非常自傲，曾憑個人自信以下犯上與大劉的兒子爭女，仍然保持優勢平分秋色。<br />\n<br />\n豪哥就係窩金，自傲有極強的引戰能力，是一個不折不扣的戰鬥狂。賢仔的好搭檔。曾經一個人用影分身術係連登四處開post挑釁是非，目的只係想單純製造混亂從而擁得快感。<br />\n<br />\n賢仔就係飛坦，平時為人沉默，表情很少變化，很難揣摩出他心裡在想什麼，和豪哥很合得來，經常一起行動。<br />\n<br />\nLocker就係依路米，設定上亦係屬於晚期加入的新團員，而且是個非常優秀的偶像派演員，做事很有原則。如同依路米擅長用念力整容，Locker亦擁有和任何女演員撞樣的能力。<br />\n<br />\n真係越諗越恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456ff09d1b217964b3a2e2413c2e6a3896e41932","tid":2346880,"uid":25260,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:54:44.000Z","msg":"Cuson 畫架喎"},{"pid":"9b1a5adf3ae1d014232186d9394c75fd670272e8","tid":2346880,"uid":372055,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:58:48.000Z","msg":"幾十歲人唔好咁多幻想啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e6a3712b6195649b82e698507e67e790b02875","tid":2346880,"uid":144014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vp9OoLN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVp9OoLN.jpg&h=d8eed6fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gzo7Ei7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzo7Ei7.jpg&h=adadffd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宇狗王耀霆呢？"},{"pid":"0288986544bbdecf39f85e11ea20fe598569969a","tid":2346880,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T23:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb46b0248644b981cf1997934ee08c7be4b4f026","tid":2346880,"uid":128884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T23:14:48.000Z","msg":"樓豬真係好中二病"},{"pid":"9a92ad33206c5066e486cef8643eda702e8126eb","tid":2346880,"uid":226739,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T23:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wiki.komica.org/images/9/9e/%E8%97%8D%E8%89%B2%E7%AA%97%E7%B0%BE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2Fimages%2F9%2F9e%2F%25E8%2597%258D%25E8%2589%25B2%25E7%25AA%2597%25E7%25B0%25BE.jpg&h=c178aa6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee066ba2932f5ffa113222fe975099318373bcd8","tid":2346880,"uid":245484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T23:30:38.000Z","msg":"作者已死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59931ff0d65ef73ea97b7947cc7cb16e02a1572","tid":2346880,"uid":76249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a92ad33206c5066e486cef8643eda702e8126eb","tid":2346880,"uid":226739,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T23:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wiki.komica.org/images/9/9e/%E8%97%8D%E8%89%B2%E7%AA%97%E7%B0%BE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2Fimages%2F9%2F9e%2F%25E8%2597%258D%25E8%2589%25B2%25E7%25AA%2597%25E7%25B0%25BE.jpg&h=c178aa6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T23:32:31.0